revision.text: ==English== ===Proper noun=== {{en-proper noun|Yancys}} # {{surname|en}}. # {{given name|en|male|from=surnames}} ===Statistics=== * According to the 2010 United States Census, ''Yancy'' is the 7580<sup>th</sup> most common surname in the United States, belonging to 4384 individuals. ''Yancy'' is most common among Black/African American (53.74%) and White (38.96%) individuals.
